node.text:
It’s Go Skate Day! Learn it with my @stompsessions Trick Tip. Voted as the most “liked” on my recent post. 

Tag #stompsessions to get your Tre Flip featured on their IG stories. 

Watch all 40+ Trick Tip videos on the Stomp app. Link in their bio. 

#goskateday #skateboard #tricktip #treflip #thankyou #skateboarding #letsgo

node.text: Couldn’t be more stoked to announce the @fallen.footwear Ripper will be dropping TONIGHT at 11:59pm PST on the Fallen U.S. & EU website. We are releasing four limited colorways with a total of about 200 pairs each with more colorways coming in the fall. Thank you all for all the support so far and hope you love the Ripper as much as I do. #RiseWithTheFallen #Fallenfootwear

node.text:
Want to learn how to Half Cab Heel Flip? Check out my @stompsessions Trick Tip Video. Link in their bio.

I’ll teach you how to dial it on flat ground, so you can take it to the streets, hitting gaps and more. 

#howto #halfcabheelflip #skateboard #tricktip #skateboarding #stompsessions 

—-

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Chris Cole on June 24, 2021. May be an image of 1 person and long hair.

node.text:
This beauty has been alive for 12,775 days. Which is 306,600 hours. That time has been spent well crafting an amazing mind, with care and beautiful creativity. Nobody is more talented across the board, from design to taste tests, pitch decks to building. I don’t know how you do it all ,even when I watch you do it all.
Most incredible is your love for your children, and being able to always focus on what’s best for them through everything that’s on your plate. 
No single person on earth has been more influential to my life, and I want to say thank you. 
Happy birthday Red! You’re fantastic.
 You like fun facts, so here’s two that happened on your birthday
1817- 1st coffee planted in Hawaii on Kona coast
1947- flying saucers spotted over mount rainier
